Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（公共电话）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.61,0:00:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.74,0:00:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事  火村学长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕一秒  我也不想让你再待在那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.35,0:00:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是自说自话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到一个没有那家伙的地方  让我们重新开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.61,0:00:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.02,0:00:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.73,0:00:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真强硬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.04,0:00:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  既然你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久濑  久濑！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久濑  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.11,0:02:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一醒过来就看见你们  我还是下地狱的好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.56,0:02:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打119吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.37,0:02:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,000就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.62,0:02:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  不用叫救护车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才  我把和瑞希的关系了结了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此分手  相信今后不会再见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像与前女友那样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:02:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不激扬青春吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.45,0:03:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们早就不是谈青春的年纪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.71,0:03:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想了结我不管
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.27,0:03:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可如果做过火的话  连回忆都会消失得一干二净
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就没有不舍得忘掉的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.11,0:03:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总还是有点快乐的经历吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.21,0:03:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边天气真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经走得很远啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  下面该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.15,0:03:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都没计划过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去填饱肚子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先逛逛房产中介
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找个住处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我就去找工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.50,0:03:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  不想吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说不吃午饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没理由要硬撑着不吃了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗  说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想出人头地了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我而抛弃人生  可不会有什么好处哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做…你早晚会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经后悔过了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.11,0:04:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不会再后悔了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说过吧  我是你的初恋情人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.27,0:04:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还说过  初恋还持续着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也是如此吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:32.78,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板  叨扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:34.67,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来啊…好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  平时都是立即回答的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.43,0:04:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过我喜欢你  这是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这一点一直都没变
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是谎言  是真心话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.40,0:04:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要忍着不眨眼  可真够累人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:58.74,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人讨厌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太勉强了  学长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连身份都说不清  谁会租房给我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说得还不够清楚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是离家出走的学生两名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身份可疑的两人这一点是够清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见鬼…找不到房子  今晚睡哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外地缺乏计划性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.33,0:05:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种突发状况下  怎么定计划啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.19,0:05:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今晚就找个旅馆住下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.17,0:05:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅馆？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀学长  你刚才往不健康的方向想了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁  谁想了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.01,0:05:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说傻话也要有个限度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得…也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.46,0:05:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那个…可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去下一家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.81,0:06:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天一定能找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去旅馆住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在找到工作前  储蓄必须得省着花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可住处要是定不下来  工作也无从谈起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是基督徒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不都是神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.14,0:06:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不懂你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢您今晚赐我们容身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏是夏天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.11,0:06:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是冬天就冻死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天的夜晚也很凉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.01,0:07:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这样一来就暖和了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.98,0:07:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就不是纯洁之身了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你是优子这一点没有变
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你变成什么样  我的心意也不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.47,0:07:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,始建20年前  四叠半的单间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:35.19,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注：叠是日本特有面积单位，大小在1.6平方米左右
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厨房卫生间一律共用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种条件  房租居然还比我之前租的地方贵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,押金礼金全免  立刻可以入住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠那种应付差事的身份证明就能租房给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经是万幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专供有难言之隐人士的公寓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.48,0:07:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来必须得注意防盗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:08:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连手机都没有的人  还有什么东西怕被盗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.39,0:08:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜的遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞节时买给她的红色手表
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…你去世妹妹的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我唯独没法丢弃它…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  写生簿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想用它来打发时间的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就是你扔给我的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…因为这个你才…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.22,0:08:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在同情我  在可怜我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想要那些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  优子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.56,0:08:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是因为那样才跟你来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:08:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.35,0:09:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  优子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真傻…居然相信了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底  你也只是把我当作自我满足的道具不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.12,0:09:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的感受  对你来说都无所谓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和明良兄长有什么区别！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.89,0:09:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子  也许你说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.14,0:09:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也和雨宫一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.61,0:10:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一直在为没能保护好茜而懊悔…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这不是同情  也不是什么可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不是用你做茜的替身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.82,0:10:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子  我只是想保护你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.10,0:10:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不会松开这双手了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:32.24,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}从天空中摇曳着飘落下一根白色羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来啦  夕君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.94,0:10:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还只是实习  没正式工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭做好了  快趁热吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.82,0:10:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯亮着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说  再怎么寒酸的公寓里也得有电灯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.15,0:11:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人住的时候  可没有过回到家里有灯亮着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家时有人在等着的感觉真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你要是回来晚了我就关灯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把门锁了睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算哭着求情也不给你开门
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  一定要早点回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕君回家的地方  也是我回家的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  这里也是我的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是个累赘哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕君至今的所有努力都付之流水了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再努力不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕君…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我画像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.21,0:12:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不擅长人物画…不过还是画画看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说和前女友分手的事时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她反倒替我哭了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我都没哭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.84,0:12:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎么…现在的我特别想哭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久濑…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有经历过挫折
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那只是因为我不会去做可能失败的事而选择逃避罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要把我扔进这个无法逃避的游戏里！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要让我去玩一场注定会输的游戏…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久濑…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颗心脏…还有瑞希…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我这个没有未来的人还能做什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底我还能再做些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久濑  我明白你的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是在崩溃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好的你们又能明白什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.11,0:13:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算你自暴自弃  也不会有什么好结果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都死到临头了  还会有什么好结果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一开始就放弃的话  你什么也得不到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想听你教训我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂得死心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没完没了地继续着已经结束的游戏的家伙又懂得什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.25,0:13:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久濑！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不会再见到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不会再见到…雨宫优子了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.03,0:13:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨宫…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挣的钱够糊口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:14:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可中途退学的你很难找工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来这干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来买包烟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想让我把优子交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你能决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  也不是我能决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.02,0:14:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道优子会想回你那里去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倘若没有别的地方可回的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.01,0:14:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也只能这样了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是没法做她的归宿的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.14,0:14:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是她的避难所  并不是真的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.14,0:14:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要问原因  那是因为你自己也一直在逃避吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有逃避！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没逃吗  那个地震的晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  你把唯一的妹妹给丢弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那天起  你就远离争斗  只是不断逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才会放开优子的手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.11,0:14:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又放弃了画画  放弃了颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避着我  逃避着曾经的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.45,0:15:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还要逃避吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底  你只是在逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你说我还能做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你自己也意识到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.54,0:15:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不小心了  买个像样点的锁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真正能做的  就是在那场地震中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.78,0:15:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你妹妹一起死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是一清二楚的  要问为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我也曾想过要那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.72,0:15:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那一天我却没有在妹妹身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是十分羡慕你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.99,0:15:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时  又十分地恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天  你和你妹妹是在一起的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  你却逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有去救你妹妹  而是逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有去和你妹妹一起死掉  而是逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:54.89,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:16:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明明是你重要的妹妹  而你却逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在恐惧和痛苦中呼唤着你  而你却逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明可以和她一起去死  而你却逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明明是衷心期盼的命运  而你却逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为她赎罪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你获得她的宽恕了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能坦然地去寻找幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又在逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来  你还会再一次失去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连自己的归宿都…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要…失去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在逃吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…又在逃了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕君  夕君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.21,0:17:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕君  你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回来吧  学长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长  火村学长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪学长  你到底在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪  学长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.37,0:17:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥…哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是想青春一把吗  这下满足了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「明明不会再见到雨宫优子了」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.85,0:20:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久濑！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.03,0:20:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不说出这句话  我死都不能瞑目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.33,0:20:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕  倒是你才不要老纠结着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做个了结吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.24,0:20:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久濑  你知道有些话能说  有些话不能说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  说来凪也还纠结着那家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.34,0:21:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好冷静一下头脑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  你会存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.92,0:21:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都有段时间没做过梦了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.39,0:21:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞希  有你的东西来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是久濑先生的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.72,0:21:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是送货的人搞错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  住址写的是这里  收件人也是瑞希哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.67,0:21:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正坏掉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:54.18,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.01,0:21:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是久濑先生吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.30,0:22:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让海风弄潮小提琴可不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.96,0:22:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼泪也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.35,0:22:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候真的很受打击
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.99,0:22:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪姐居然说自己是女朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.76,0:22:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算硬让两人分开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.43,0:22:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要心灵依旧相通  就没办法了结关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.56,0:22:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了结…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱的时候  如果自己坠入情网就算输了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.89,0:22:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要让对方爱上自己才行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.40,0:22:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是久濑的口头禅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.38,0:22:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然充满久濑先生的风格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这次不同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.98,0:22:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是被你爱上了  可就要输了的却是久濑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.49,0:22:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事…输到体无完肤的是我才对…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.31,0:22:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌…好想哭…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.59,0:23:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.78,0:23:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙从来只打必胜之仗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.88,0:23:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他赢不了输了还能再站起来的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.91,0:23:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够拯救那家伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.28,0:23:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就只有你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.53,0:23:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意料外的邂逅  让心支离破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.11,0:23:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ef - a tale of melodies
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,return
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.25,0:23:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能听到吗？  ——那真实的旋律


